                        Trainer for Breathless v1.1
                        ---------------------------
Very useful running utility for game Breathless. You can edit weapons,
boosts, keys, health, credits, energy, shield, starting world and arena,
prices of any equipment. Unlimited health, energy, shield, credits and keys
can be selected. Crack option is here too.

Trainer is only for version 1.1 of Breathless. Both versions (for 020/030 -
normal and for 060) are accepted.

How to use:
Copy this trainer to directory with Breathless game. After running and
selecting of your configuration press "OK..." button to run Breathless.
More informations can be found in "Instructions" window in trainer.

Good luck!

